original_query: SELECT g.nid, pw.nid FROM symptom s, presents pres, disease d, downregulates down, gene g, participates p, pathway pw WHERE s.nid = pres.tid AND pres.sid = d.nid AND d.nid = down.sid AND down.tid = g.nid AND g.nid = p.sid AND p.tid = pw.nid
rewritten_query: CREATE VIEW E4 AS SELECT downregulates.sid AS E4_sid,downregulates.tid AS E4_tid FROM downregulates AS downregulates
CREATE VIEW E3 AS SELECT disease.nid AS E3_nid FROM disease AS disease
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage1_0 AS SELECT * FROM E4 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3 WHERE E4.E4_sid=E3.E3_nid)
CREATE VIEW E5 AS SELECT gene.nid AS E5_nid FROM gene AS gene
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage1_1 AS SELECT * FROM E4_stage1_0 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E5 WHERE E4_stage1_0.E4_tid=E5.E5_nid)
CREATE VIEW E6 AS SELECT participates.sid AS E6_sid,participates.tid AS E6_tid FROM participates AS participates
CREATE VIEW E7 AS SELECT pathway.nid AS E7_nid FROM pathway AS pathway
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E6_stage1_0 AS SELECT * FROM E6 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E7 WHERE E6.E6_tid=E7.E7_nid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage1_2 AS SELECT * FROM E4_stage1_1 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E6_stage1_0 WHERE E4_stage1_1.E4_tid=E6_stage1_0.E6_sid)
CREATE VIEW E2 AS SELECT presents.sid AS E2_sid,presents.tid AS E2_tid FROM presents AS presents
CREATE VIEW E1 AS SELECT symptom.nid AS E1_nid FROM symptom AS symptom
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E2_stage1_0 AS SELECT * FROM E2 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E1 WHERE E2.E2_tid=E1.E1_nid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage1_3 AS SELECT * FROM E4_stage1_2 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E2_stage1_0 WHERE E4_stage1_2.E4_sid=E2_stage1_0.E2_sid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E3_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E3 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4_stage1_3 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_sid=E3.E3_nid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E5_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E5 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4_stage1_3 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_tid=E5.E5_nid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E6_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E6_stage1_0 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4_stage1_3 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_tid=E6_stage1_0.E6_sid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E7_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E7 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E6_stage2_0 WHERE E6_stage2_0.E6_tid=E7.E7_nid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E2_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E2_stage1_0 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4_stage1_3 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_sid=E2_stage1_0.E2_sid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E1_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E1 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E2_stage2_0 WHERE E2_stage2_0.E2_tid=E1.E1_nid)

CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E_stage3 AS SELECT E5_stage2_0.E5_nid AS E5_nid FROM E4_stage1_3, E3_stage2_0, E5_stage2_0, E6_stage2_0, E7_stage2_0, E2_stage2_0, E1_stage2_0 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_sid=E3_stage2_0.E3_nid AND E4_stage1_3.E4_tid=E5_stage2_0.E5_nid AND E6_stage2_0.E6_tid=E7_stage2_0.E7_nid AND E4_stage1_3.E4_tid=E6_stage2_0.E6_sid AND E2_stage2_0.E2_tid=E1_stage2_0.E1_nid AND E4_stage1_3.E4_sid=E2_stage2_0.E2_sid
SELECT * FROM E_stage3
